{"tid":703151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚到尿滲] 批美反覆挑起貿易戰　華商務部：中方將強有力回擊","createTime":"2018-06-15T13:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T05:34:19.000Z","uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c657cfed8930177a0d46d02ba14dd060483ca68b","tid":703151,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bknint-20180615204236401-0615_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180615%2Fbknint-20180615204236401-0615_17011_001.html&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05Zif7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9557cafb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180615/bknint-20180615204236401-0615_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周五（15日）正式宣布，對總值500億美元（約3900億港元）的中國進口商品徵收25%關稅。中國商務部新聞發言人同日回應事件，指美國置雙方已形成的共識不顧，反覆無常並挑起貿易戰，損害雙邊利益和破壞世界貿易秩序；更重申中方面對美方損人不利已的短視行為，不得不予以強有力回擊。商務部續稱，將立即推出同等規模、同等力度的徵稅措施，雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果，亦將同時失效。 <br />\n<br />\n商務部發言人表示，中美雙方曾就經貿問題開展多輪磋商，力圖解決分歧，實現雙贏；又指美方反覆無常並挑起貿易戰，損害雙邊利益，也破壞世界貿易秩序，對此中方堅決反對。商務部稱，中方並不想打貿易戰，但面對美方損人不利已的短視行為，中方不得不予以強有力回擊，堅決捍衞國家利益和人民利益，堅決捍衞經濟全球化和多邊貿易體制。商務部重申，當今時代發起貿易戰，不符合全球利益，當局呼籲各國採取共同行動，制止相關行為。"},{"pid":"ebaf392a6956b64a50d6622970edb87ad6612a70","tid":703151,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/yellow.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f379697458bb801240e0daa6cf8d2951a24e4d","tid":703151,"uid":78143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif&h=197902a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"696be264e7d7e21b4e1b9f830c8b58d2c46d5dfc","tid":703151,"uid":182499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:59:42.000Z","msg":"上次史詩級 今次強有力回擊 下次終極報復呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8294060ee9b247788137c8c0d9a2fbc17bfa6a","tid":703151,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"//雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果，亦將同時失效。 //<br />\n<br />\n之前有咩成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9684fbf5e2beadd8ec1d72679422419e9f53975","tid":703151,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"08f379697458bb801240e0daa6cf8d2951a24e4d","tid":703151,"uid":78143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif&h=197902a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/67/1443309886-2940079167.gif/revision/latest?cb=20160406163950\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F67%2F1443309886-2940079167.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20160406163950&h=33214762&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9daba719d02a213ed7e0dd9eaa34f2888737802b","tid":703151,"uid":37413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"支那狗本身就冇合約精神不守信用啦<br />\n明明簽咗中英聯合聲明又話冇效<br />\n其他對香港人嘅承諾亦冇實現過"},{"pid":"6f8b16f2d273dd9e11f355aa00d845d43406dc15","tid":703151,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd19b279665bf58c767a14dd92ec914344601235","tid":703151,